description._content: Description: Interior of one of the twin Pump-Houses at Tembi, shewing the two turbine-driven centrifugal oil-pumps. Location: Tembi, Persia Description: Interior of the Power-House at Tembi, Showing the electric generators-the two nearest the camera being turbine-driven. Location: Tembi, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown. We have attempted to provide place information for the images automatically but our software may not have found the correct location.
